<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.8.3">
<l>karuḷak koṭiyoṉ ṟuṭaiyīr taṉippākīr</l>
<l>uruḷac cakaṭa matuṟak kilnimirttīr</l>
<l>maruḷaik koṭupā ṭivantil lampukuntīr</l>
<l>iruḷat tituveṉ ṉituveṉ ṉituveṉṉō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who has a Garuḍa banner, unique rider,</l>
<l>You straightened out in [your] sleep so that a cart rolled over;</l>
<l>You entered our yard, having arrived singing, with a love song</l>
<l>In the dark! What is this? What is this? What is this?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
